lead_paragraph: First Stephen Vogt delivered the lineup card to the umpires. Then he connected for a three-run home run that helped the Oakland Athletics beat the St. Louis Cardinals 7-4 Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Triggs Earns First Win as Athletics Power Past Cardinals 7-4
